                     <interp inst="t18310407-130-person1097" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner, and have the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310407-130-person1098">
                  JAMES 
                  ALEXANDER
               <interp inst="t18310407-130-person1098" type="surname" value="ALEXANDER"></interp>
